translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,16,Jo kehtay hain kay aey humaray rab! Hum eman laa chukay iss liey humaray gunah moaf farma aur humen aag kay azab say bacha
  3,17,Jo sabar kerney walay aur sach bolney walay aur farmanbardari kerney walay aur Allah ki raah mein kharach kerney walay aur pichli raat ko baksish maangney walay hain
  3,18,Allah Taalaa farishtay aur ehal-e-ilm iss baat ki gawahi detay hain kay Allah kay siwa koi mabood nahi aur woh adal ko qaeem rakhney wala hai uss ghalib aur hikmata walay kay siwa koi ibadat kay laeeq nahi
  3,19,Be-shak Allah Taalaa kay nazdeek deen islam hi hai aur ehal-e-kitab ney apney pass ilm aa janey kay baad aapas ki sirkashi aur hasad ki bina per hi ikhtilaf kiya hai aur Allah Taalaa ki aayaton kay sath jo bhi kufur keray Allah Taalaa uss ka jald hisab lenay wala hai
  3,20,Phir bhi agar yeh aap say jhagren to aap keh den kay mein aur meray tabey daaron ney Allah Taalaa kay samney apna sir tasleem khum ker diya hai aur ehal-e-kitab say aur un-parh logon say keh dijiye! Kay kiya tum bhi itaâ€™at kertay ho? Pus agar yeh bhi tabye daar bann jayen to yaqeenan hidayat walay hain aur agar yeh roo gardani keren to aap per sirf phoncha dena hai aur Allah bandon ko khoob dekh bhaal raha hai
  3,21,Jo log Allah Taalaa ki aayaton say kufur kertay hain aur na haq nabiyon ko qatal ker daaltay hain aur jo log adal-o-insaf ki baat kahen unhen bhi qatal ker daaltay hain to aey nabi! Enhen dard naak azab ki khabar dey dijiye
  3,22,Inn kay aemaal duniya-o-aakhirat mein ghaarat hain aur inn ka koi madadgar nahi